Title: Relates to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "T Sgt. Walter Shearing Memorial Highway"
Summary: Designates a portion of the state highway system in the village of Gainesville as the "T Sgt. Walter Shearing Memorial Highway".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "T Sgt. Walter Shearing Memorial Highway"
